Qaddafi's Son Says Libya May Become `Like Somalia' If Peace Isn't Restored

-- B y   Z a h r a   H a n k i r
-- 
2011-02-26T17:56:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-26/qaddafi-s-son-says-libya-may-become-like-somalia-if-peace-isn-t-restored.html
Saif al-Islam Qaddafi, son of Libyan
leader  Muammar Qaddafi , said the country should move towards a
regime change and a new constitution peacefully after his father
called for the changes.  Otherwise,  Libya  “risks becoming like  Somalia ,” he said
in an interview on Al-Arabiya television today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Zahra Hankir in Dubai at 
